Prolog interpreter

data type
variable (% sym num) to avoid lack of memory

data base   symbol (set-property '((foo a)) 'prolog 'foo)  predicate
                   (set-property '(((foo _x)(bar _x))) 'prolog 'foo)  clause

variable _name e.g. _x _y _z
anoymous _
